title: Which 2017 Latin Song Is Your Favorite (So Far): 'Despacito' or 'Subeme la Radio'? Vote!
text:
Courtesy Photo Luis Fonsi ft. Daddy Yankee "Despacito" 
It has only been two months since the beginning of the year, and many Latin superstars already have surprised us with new music we will be listening all year. 
From Nicky Jam to Enrique Iglesias , see below the artists who have released a song (so far) and vote for your favorite! 
In case you missed a song, listen to it below:
